by_statement: čhattham dōi Sathāban Wičhai læ Phatthanā Mahāwitthayālai Khō̜n Kǣn ; sanapsanun dōi khrōngkān ʻanurak læ phatthanā pāmai thī yangyư̄n nai khēt raksā phan satpā Phū Khīeo dōi mīsūanrūam khō̜ng chumchon.

description.value: Study on the situations, trend of change and factors influence of cow-raising of communities surrounds Phu Khieo Wildlife Sanctuary, Khon Kaen Province, Northeastern Thailand.
